                     <interp inst="t18430130-747-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>for feloniously receiving, of an evil-disposed person, on the <rs id="t18430130-cd-152" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430130-747-offence-1 t18430130-cd-152"></join>14th of Jan</rs>., 30lbs. weight of lead, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18430130-name-936" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18430130-name-936" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
